results.name: a(n) = Min { k | A064920(k) = n }.
comment: A064920(a(n)) = n. a(n) = n iff n is prime.
link: Harry J. Smith, Table of n, a(n) for n = 2..1000
program: (PARI) gpf(n)= { local(f); f=factor(n)~; return(f[1, length(f)]) } { for (n=2, 1000, k=1; until (m==n, k++; g=gpf(k); m=k / g + g - 1); write("b064923.txt", n, " ", k) ) } \\ _Harry J. Smith_, Sep 29 2009
